author: cdupoirieux
msg: (FOR-388, FOR-742) This version implement a fall back mecanism :
- For an unversionned plugin, it try to get it from :
- if not found : the remote site in the forrest version directory
- if not found : the remote site (with no forrest version dir)
- For a versionned plugin, it tries to get :
- the versionned plugin from different local sources directory (project.required.plugins.src property)
- if not found : the versionned plugin from the remote site in the forrest version directory
- if not found : the unversionned plugin in different local sources directory (project.required.plugins.src property)
- if not found : the unversionned plugin from the remote site in the forrest version directory
- if not found : the remote site (with no forrest version dir)
